      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my reliable daily driver and it's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you. It drives smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for someone who wants a quality car without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'd love to see this go to a good home!",
