    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for the chassis longevity of this platform. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with enthusiastic road use, the suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the precise turn-in response this chassis is known for. A true driver\u2019s specification optimized for performance over concours presentation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
