      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of its class, offering a perfect balance of reliability and style. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep shine, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips one would expect from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats are supple and free of any significant wear or tears, and all power features\u2014including the sunroof and premium audio system\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a recent full service and a fresh set of tires. It tracks straight, brakes firmly, and the transmission delivers smooth, confident shifts. We have kept a comprehensive folder of service records to provide the next owner with peace of mind. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
