      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a standard of quality and performance tailored for the discerning driver. This motorcar has been curated to ensure mechanical reliability and aesthetic appeal, featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior finish. It represents a sophisticated choice for those who demand consistent performance and a professional presence on the road. This acquisition offers an exceptional balance of longevity and value.",
